Company Overview of RobecoSAM AG



Snapshot People




Company Overview
RobecoSAM AG is a privately owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to individuals, banks, insurance companies, pension funds, family offices, and trusts. It manages separate client-focused portfolios. The firm also manages equity mutual funds for its clients. It invests in public equity across the globe. The firm invests in the securities of companies across all market capitalization. It employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with a focus on sustainability trends such as demographics, climate change, industry specific challenges, and companies that develop and market innovative products to make its investments. The firm conducts in-house research to ...
RobecoSAM AG is a privately owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to individuals, banks, insurance companies, pension funds, family offices, and trusts. It manages separate client-focused portfolios. The firm also manages equity mutual funds for its clients. It invests in public equity across the globe. The firm invests in the securities of companies across all market capitalization. It employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with a focus on sustainability trends such as demographics, climate change, industry specific challenges, and companies that develop and market innovative products to make its investments. The firm conducts in-house research to make its investments. It was formerly known as SAM Sustainable Asset Management AG. The firm operates as a subsidiary of Robeco Alternative Investments. RobecoSAM AG was founded in 1995 and is based in Zurich, Switzerland with an additional office in Central, Hong Kong.
Detailed Description


