RobecoSAM is an international investment company with a specific focus on sustainability investments.[1] The company is based in Zurich, Switzerland and considers economic, environmental and social criteria in its investment strategies. In addition to asset management, the company has an indexes and private equity portion of the business.[2] RobecoSAM has a series of products based on themes such as water, energy, climate, agriculture, and healthy living.[3] In 2006 RobecoSAM introduced a division called sustainability services that provides sustainability benchmarking reports to companies.[4] In 2001, RobecoSAM became the first carbon neutral company in Switzerland.[5]



